# ── Go ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Vendored & curated from github/gitignore (Go.gitignore) — CC0-1.0.
# NOTE: go.mod and go.sum are COMMITTED — not ignored. vendor/ is usually committed too.

# Binaries
*.exe
*.exe~
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib

# Test binary / output
*.test
*.out

# Build output
/bin/
/dist/

# Go workspace checksum
go.work.sum
